ActBudget Implementation Act, 2022, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing December 30, 2022 as the Day on which Division 16 of Part 5 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2022, No. 1 Come into Force
PrecisOrder Fixing December 30, 2022 as the Day on which Division 16 of Part 5 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2022, No. 1 COMES INTO FORCE in order to extend certain terms of copyright protection from 50 years to 70 years after the life of the author.
